originalText.text: Dr Parcells and her entire staff are the best. They have made me comfortable from the first time I walked into the office. Her staff never fails to answer me on the Klara portal almost instantly whenever I have any questions. They have been there for me since before I had surgery and the surgery itself was the smoothest experience ever ! After surgery Dr Parcells and her staff have continuously checked up on me and have been very helpful during my recovery. They’re the best ! Best decision I ever made was going with Dr Parcells for my breast reduction.

originalText.text: Simply put - you just don't find doctors and practices like this often, especially in NYC. Dr. Parcells made me feel informed and safe going into my breast reduction and the surgery and recovery went exactly as planned. I am thrilled with the result and felt the impact instantly. Dr. Parcells’ team cannot go unmentioned - they’re far and away the best medical staff I’ve worked with. They are extremely responsive, communicative, kind and understanding when asking even the smallest or silliest of questions. They made me feel like with me every step of the way from submitting paperwork to monitoring pain & healing post-op.  I could go on and on about my experience Dr. Parcells and her team! Fully recommend Dr. Parcells - 10/10 - no notes!

originalText.text: Dr. Alexis Parcells is an exceptional plastic surgeon who performed my breast reduction surgery with utmost skill and care. From the initial consultation to the post-operative follow-ups, her and her team displayed a remarkable level of professionalism and compassion. Dr. Parcells took the time to understand my concerns and desires, and she delivered results that exceeded my expectations. I highly recommend Dr. Alexis Parcells to anyone considering breast reduction surgery!!
